  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>At 10th level, a hunter gains @Compendium[pf1.spells.barb21n7r3wx8cql]{Raise Animal Companion}&nbsp;as a spell-like ability; this is not restricted to raising only her own animal companion. Using this spell-like ability gives the hunter a permanent negative level. This negative level cannot be overcome in any way (including by&nbsp;restoration), but automatically ends after 24 hours.</p>\n<p>At 16th level, this functions as&nbsp;resurrection&nbsp;instead of&nbsp;raise dead, but otherwise operates as normal.</p>",
